content: That's really helpful, thank you! I'll definitely look into those options. Since I've been trying to prioritize my tasks better, I've been making a to-do list the night before, which has been helping me stay focused and avoid procrastination. To ensure I arrived on time, I woke up 1 hour before I needed to be at the office, which gave me enough time to get ready and even grab a cup of coffee before my meeting. Do you have any suggestions on how to stay organized and focused throughout the day?
